* A. Klotz, "Der Annalist Q. Claudius Quadrigarius." ''Rheinische Museum'' 91 (1942) 268-285.
* E. Badian, "The Early Historians" in T. Dorey (ed.) ''Latin Historians'' (1966) 1-38.

