'''Xanthicus''' is the name of the sixth month of the Macedonian calendar of the [[Seleucid]] Syrians.<ref>{{cite web |title=Xanthicus |url=https://www.biblicalcyclopedia.com/X/xanthicus.html |website=McClintock and Strong Biblical Cyclopedia |accessdate=23 September 2018}}</ref> It corresponds with [[Nisan]] in the [[Jewish calendar]] or April in the [[Gregorian calendar]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Xanthicus |url=https://www.biblegateway.com/resources/encyclopedia-of-the-bible/Xanthicus |website=Bible Gateway |accessdate=23 September 2018}}</ref>

